                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 161.) I saw the prisoner drop the book in Broad-street, as the prosecutor caught hold of him—I then chased, and took him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Was there no mob came round when you took me? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, there was.</p>
               <p>
